    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，从B分出两条路径到同一个Education_GradeSync节点，但标注不同：一条是chain，代表链式调用；另一条是attestation，代表认证流程。这两条路径最终都要汇合。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，B到C标注chain，B到D标注attestation，C和D都是GradeSync。画好了。接下来这两个节点要连到哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
