      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "F要连到H，H是ContentCDN的决策点，判断存储类型。这里有两个分支：self-hosted走Education_StudentDB，SaaS走最后一个Education_ClassroomService。",
