    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，H是ContentCDN的决策节点，负责分发策略判断。self-hosted走I即StudentDB本地存储，SaaS走J即ClassroomService云端处理。",
