      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "H到I标注self-hosted，H到J标注SaaS。整个流程画完了，我检查一下：A→B，B分chain/attestation到C/D，C/D→E，E分yes/no到F/G，F→H，H分self-hosted/SaaS到I/J。结构正确吗？",
