      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "理解了。最后确认一下边的标注：B→C是chain，B→D是attestation，E→F是yes，E→G是no，H→I是self-hosted，H→J是SaaS。还有其他标注吗？",
